description: Following the increase in offences and crimes in the United States, the prisons are overcrowded. To cope with the problem, the American Government tests a new prison for the most dangerous criminals: the Deepwaterprison, a maritime abyss just off the Bermudas. Nine hundred metres higher, on the surface, an oil rig explodes and sinks, creating an unprecedented ecological catastrophe. A repair team is urgently sent into the deep waters. The only place to stay at this depth is the Deepwaterprison, where mutineers are planning their escape.
name: Constellation

description: Following a murder, the Viking chief Erik the Red is banished from Iceland for 3 years. He then jumps into a crazy race with only his family as company, his animals and Leif, his faithful lieutenant, used to surviving in the most hostile environments. Their goal: finding Greenland. But even for hardened warriors such an expedition is no pleasure cruise…
name: Le Sang des Vikings

description:
NO ONE KNOWS THE ORIGIN OF THE CITY OF GASKERR, OR WHY IT WAS BUILT.

Twelve thousand inhabitants spread over 3 levels based on their social class have lived there completely autarkic for centuries, without ever leaving the protective walls. There is no prison in Gaskerr and , when faced with the problem of overpopulation, expulsion is an excellent way of controlling the demography. And outside the city, awaits certain death… At least, that’s what everyone thinks. But when young Haven is thrown out he has no other choice but to fight to survive.
name: Exil

description: Tuena, Haven and Ghaerr progress towards Dawndark and the secrets of the past clear slowly. The race to survive transforms itself quickly into a quest for truth and justice. A strange destiny links our trio, but in order to discover it they will have to brave a thousand perils and make it to Athuya, where everything seems to converge to.
name: Les 3 Clefs

description:
This issue consists of a hand painted figurine and a magazine on the issues featured character, Brainiac

The Justice League set ends with issue 64, Black Pawn - Brainiac.
name: Brainiac

description:
If the war is still waging in 1947, it is particularly due to the major setback for the Allies that was the catastrophe of 6th June 1944 in Normandy.
Follow with Murnau, a brilliant officer of the Luftwaffe at the commands of his Messerschmitt 262 fighter, the events of a disaster which has since been called in the free world, Disaster Day.
name: Disaster day

description: Everyone had decided that Dyssery would marry Phorée. Everyone except Dyssery. To escape the marriage, the beautiful woman kills herself. She is now in the Valley of the Shadows, where the souls of the dead are much freer than in the land of the living. But Phorée isn’t done yet and counts on getting his fiancée back.

The Vigilantes have joined up again to stop William Peter Stahl from aiming at one of the highest posts in the State.

Back in Pitsgreen, the town where it all began, they find the full use of their “super powers”, and the memories of their first battle against the bloodthirsty killer reopen old and terrifying wounds… and awaken a new threat…
name: Retour à Pitsgreen

description: In Greece, Achilles, son of Peleus, and Tyndareos, king of Sparta, go against Agamemnon, the lord of Mycenae. As war seems inevitable, a gigantic army from the Orient menaces the Hittite empire and the all powerful Egypt of Ramses II. No one seems capable of defeating these warriors carried by the magic of Ouranos, a God once banished by Zeus. The Delphic oracle, Pythia, prophesizes that the world’s future will be decided in the city of Troy.
name: Le peuple de la mer

description:
Courage, solidarity, respect.
The Top Team is a rugby team made up from 14 of the best hopefuls of each club of the French elite. The team will proudly wear the colors of all the Top 14 clubs by going up against its European rivals and try to win the “Team Challenge” shield. For their risky undertaking, they will have the precious advice of the emblematic players of the French championships like Wilkinson, Kockott, Picamoles, Tales… and they have their support too !
name: La Top Team

description: A small island in the middle of the Pacific. Thalulaa and her sister, the island shaman’s daughters, fi nd a blonde young man with Celtic tattoos washed up on the beach. The villagers take in this stranger who seems to have forgotten everything...
name: Manta Oro

description:
Reconnect with Thalulaa and her companions in the exciting sequel of their adventures…

Lost in the net of time, Thalulaa and her friends will try and restore order to all the temporal mesh. But they have to get out of it themselves and find the path out of time, in order to allow them to find their families… At different time periods, other characters are on the same quest. But do they have the same goal?
name: Alizées temporelles

description:
1130, three Templers discover a door behind which is an inestimable treasure. But only one of them will survive long enough to give a Bedouin a map and his testimony.

Fifty years later, five characters, Conan Meriadec, from the backwoods of Brittany, Frédéric from the Order of Malta, Jean the poet, Lubin the monk and Orient of Saint-Sulpice the Templer are seeking to find the ancient door.
name: Dans les murailles de Tyr

description:
The sequel of our heroes at the doors of the Holy Land…

Our protagonists, Conan from little Brittany, Lubin the fallen Hospitable monk, Frédéric the Maltese, Jean the Poet. And Orient of Saint-Sulpice the Templar, now possess the map that will lead them to the doors of Baphomet in the Sinai desert.

All five of them have a different reason for finding Lucifer’s gold.

But one of them is secretly working for the Templar’s enemy: the black company.

Stuck in Tyr, town under siege by Saladin, who also covets the map, they will have to show great prowess to succeed in their quest.
name: Dans la tourmente

volume.name: Yuppies, Rednecks, and Lesbian Bitches on Mars

description: Idomenus and Aeson are the biggest investigators of the Greek world, the Sherlock and Watson of mythological antiquity. They have to get their hand on the person who tried to sabotage the capital’s locks in the Atlantide kingdom. Who is trying to take the atlant empirical throne at the risk of provoking a cataclysm that would engulf the entire continent under water?
name: The Prince with Golden Crabs

description:
1983. An island in the Pacific. One morning, an intense light spreads in the fraction of a second... The inhabitants life just got turned upside down and their memories seem to be erased...
25 years later: Los Angeles. Jonathan Caldwell sometimes feels blinded by green luminous halos and his dreams, that have become nightmares, seem way too real...
name: Absences
